features: 【Ultra Soft & Breathable】The queen size comforter sets have premium microfiber fabric which is breathable and sweat-absorbent. The queen size comforter inner is filled with 260 GSM microfiber to meet your various sleeping posture requirements and always remains lightweight and fluffy, and the cloud-like softness of the dark grey queen comforter sets with sheets and pillows keeps you comfortable and warm every night in all seasons.

【Stylish & Durable】Queen bed in a bag is designed with delicate box stitching, simple but classic. This bedding set looks very decorative and helps evenly distribute the fiberfill and prevent shifting for maximum durability and a deluxe feel. The solid bed in a bag queen size is suitable for any room in your house as a perfect decor.

【Size of Comforter Set】Newspin 8 piece comforter set queen size has 4 sizes available. Queen comforter set with sheets includes 1 Comforter (90" x 90"), 2 Pillow Shams (20" x 26" + 2"), 1 Flat Sheet (92" x 102"), 1 Fitted Sheet (60" x 80" + 14"), 2 Pillowcases (20" x 30" + 4"), 1 Bed Skirt (60" x 80"+ 15"). Since our bedding set comes in vacuum-sealed packaging, it is highly recommended to dry it in low heat or hang out the bedding set in the sun and gently tap it for increased fluffiness.

【Lavish & Practical Details】A luxury feel thanks to details. The 360° elastic fitted sheet is about 1"-16" deep. Twin bedding sets have a solid flat sheet and a bed skirt complements the bed, while the pillow shams feature flanges. It's a great choice as a Mother's Day, Birthday, Christmas, New Year or Back to School gift for teens, boys, girls, men or women.

【Perfect For All Seasons】Newspin queen bed in a bag keeps you comfortable all year round! The 8 pieces queen comforter set is designed with breathability in mind, the appropriate filling offers a good puff to keep you warm and cozy for all seasons and will let you away from sweat and keep your body fresh all night long. Our bed comforter set keeps you warm in the winter and cool in the summer.

【Easy Care & Satisfactory Service】The bedding sets can be easily cleaned in a washing machine. To ensure year-round softness and prevent the formation of pills, we highly recommend washing them using the gentle cycle with cold water, followed by sun-drying or tumble drying on low when necessary. A supremely comfortable comforter set guarantees a restful sleep for you! Please do not hesitate to reach out to us if you have any inquiries regarding our products.

reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I recently purchased the Newspin King Bed in a Bag 8 Pieces Comforter Set in black, and I couldn't be happier with my choice. It keeps me warm during colder nights without causing overheating during warmer months, ensuring a comfortable sleep throughout the year.Complete Bedding Solution: I love that this set includes everything I need for my bed – a comforter, pillow shams, flat sheet, fitted sheet, pillowcases, and a bed skirt. It's a comprehensive solution that saves me the hassle of purchasing individual pieces separately.Quality Fabric: The fabric used in this bedding set is soft to the touch and feels luxurious. The attention to detail in the design is evident, enhancing the overall aesthetics of my bed.Great Value: Considering the number of pieces included in the set and the quality of the fabric, I find this bedding set to be an excellent value for the price. It's a cost-effective way to update the look and feel of my bedroom.In conclusion, the Newspin King Bed in a Bag 8 Pieces Comforter Set has exceeded my expectations in terms of quality, design, and comfort. It has transformed my bedroom into a cozy and stylish retreat.
